                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Bowen</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Caracas</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-03-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 25, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Bowen reports that Señor Paul cabled to Venezuelan President on the 24th
                    that the Government of the United States will not answer Mr. Bowen, or will give
                    him conciliatory instructions.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
